Definition: a test performed at home in which you collect specimens of your stool that are tested for traces of blood
Example: used to detect colorectal cancers
Synonyms: faecal_occult_test, stool_test, diagnostic_test, a, test, performed, at, home, in, which, you, collect, specimens, of, your, stool, that, are, tested, for, traces, blood, used, to, detect, colorectal, cancers
Category: noun.cognition
